      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I hear that. But it feels like the 'pro-innovation' argument is often just a shield they use to avoid being held accountable for how they actually crush everyone else. Do you think the investigations are actually catching up to how these companies have been operating, or is the government just trying to pick winners and losers?",
